  <brief_title>Safety Study of Airway Clearance Techniques in Infants.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Bouncing, Assisted Autogenic Drainage (AAD) and Bouncing Combined With AAD on Gastro-esophageal Reflux ( GOR ), Oxygen Saturation (SaO2) and Heart Rate in Infants From 0 to 12 Months</official_title>
  <sponsors>
