  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether three airway clearance techniques (
      Bouncing, Assisted Autogenic Drainage ( AAD) and bouncing combined with AAD) provoke or
      aggravate gastro-esophageal reflux in infants under the age of 1 year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
